OL,3,CPeter Kay to perform 'locals only'
OL,4,Chomecoming charity shows
OL,6,FPeter Kay is returning to his hometown
OL,7,Fafter 23 years for a set of charity
OL,8,Fgigs for locals only.
OL,10,FThe comedian will be performing four
OL,11,Fshows in July 2026 at The Albert Halls
OL,12,Fin Bolton for the first time since
OL,13,F2003.
OL,15,FAll profits from the surprise shows
OL,16,Fwill be donated to Bolton Hospice,
OL,17,Fwhich Peter Kay described as an
OL,18,F"amazing charity".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
