OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776712270
OL,3,CPeter Kay to perform 'locals only'
OL,4,Chomecoming charity shows
OL,6,FThe shows will take place between the
OL,7,F9-11 July 2026, with tickets going on
OL,8,Fsale at 10am on Friday 24 April.
OL,10,FHowever, only a select few will be
OL,11,Feligible to buy tickets - with sales
OL,12,Flimited to fans who live at a BL
OL,13,Fpostcode.
OL,15,FPeter said: "I can't believe it's 23
OL,16,Fyears since my Albert Halls shows, so
OL,17,FI reckon it's about time I came back.
OL,18,FI'm really looking forward to it.
OL,26,@wD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
