PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776712270
OL,3,CPeter Kay to perform 'locals only'
OL,4,Chomecoming charity shows
OL,6,F"The shows are a thank you to the
OL,7,Fpeople of Bolton for their support
OL,8,Fover the years but especially Bolton
OL,9,FHospice, which is an amazing charity
OL,10,Fand would not be able to provide the
OL,11,Fhelp it does without donations."
OL,13,FChair of Bolton Hospice, Judith
OL,14,FBromley, said: "What a fantastic
OL,15,Fsurprise this is - we can't thank
OL,16,FPeter enough for his ongoing support
OL,17,Fof the hospice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@`O]vD@POU
