OL,3,CPeter Kay to perform 'locals only'
OL,4,Chomecoming charity shows
OL,6,F"The money raised from these shows in
OL,7,FBolton will make a huge difference to
OL,8,Fall the local people who use our vital
OL,9,Fservices."
OL,11,FThe venue featured in his iconic
OL,12,Fcomedy special "Peter Kay: Live at the
OL,13,FBolton Albert Halls", which is still
OL,14,Fthe UK's best selling stand-up DVD of
OL,15,Fall time.
